SEASONED DJ Euphonik has taken a swipe at trolls who mock celebrities but also wish they were famous. The star posted a cheeky tweet, in which he said the only reason twitter trolls were mad at stars was because they secretly wanted to be like them. “They hate famous people. But they want to be famous themselves,” tweeted the star whose real name is Themba Nkosi. His tweet left his followers speculating about who trolled him. Euphonik has been posting a series of pictures of himself in Germany. While SAA has said international travel will only be allowed back in September, the property tycoon used a private jet. They hate famous people but they want to be famous themselves ??  